QuestData.Title: Into the Vale
QuestData.Description: Ah, I have been waiting for your arrival, traveler.$B$BI wish we could meet in better times, but alas, I fear the situation in the Vale is quite dire.$B$BBut let us not speak of that now. Go visit Madam Vee Luo at the Shrine of Two Moons.$B$BShe should be able to settle you in.
QuestData.LogDescription: Speak to Madam Vee Luo at the Shrine of Two Moons in the Vale of Eternal Blossoms.
